{"tid":1563963,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"打機淨係做支線係永遠都爆唔到機，記得做返正經嘢。","createTime":"2019-09-12T14:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T01:20:40.000Z","uid":102089,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"b758e11e158b4cbeb9d25e08fcf5bd77703571c7","tid":1563963,"uid":102089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:58:45.000Z","msg":"之後開過個機場post，不過唔識推秒沉，今次唔知有冇人睇到。<br />\n<br />\n唱歌還唱歌，唔好唔記得正經野，打機淨係做支線係<span style=\"color: red;\">永遠都爆唔到機</span>。人哋藍絲已經有晒組織，入面重有啲高級藍色讀撚飽書對付我地。又捉跳閘，又組隊拆連儂牆，今日重有IFC唱中國國歌！<br />\n<br />\n請各位手足<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好輕敵</span>，唔好沉醉於唱歌呢個開心嘅氣氛入面，一齊唱歌係好撚開心，不過再係咁懶懶閒落去，同慢性自殺冇分別。唔好諗住做左少少嘢就當做左，麻煩請大家行多步。<br />\n<br />\n平時<span style=\"color: red;\">唔出嚟</span>嘅，就去<span style=\"color: red;\">join下唱歌</span>。<br />\n平時<span style=\"color: red;\">有唱歌</span>嘅，就去下<span style=\"color: red;\">遊行集會</span>。<br />\n去開<span style=\"color: red;\">遊行集會</span>嘅，就幫手做下<span style=\"color: red;\">文宣</span>。<br />\n有做開<span style=\"color: red;\">文宣</span>嘅，就開個<span style=\"color: red;\">twitter</span>打外國戰線。<br />\n再想做多啲嘢，就搵下其他巴絲啲post，應該詳盡過我。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">星期日</span>係國際民主日，記得出嚟行街！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2xgafp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz2xgafp.png&h=91fbff3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v6F15OL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv6F15OL.png&h=5a6ba203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Lmpi8L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Lmpi8L.jpg&h=f9ff82bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cHMs1m6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcHMs1m6.jpg&h=e23f0b0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。</span></span>"},{"pid